### 1. Create a new Order (Client)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}

{
  "pickupAddress": "Times Square, NY",
  "destinationAddress": "Empire State Building, NY",
  "pickupLat": 40.7580,
  "pickupLon": -73.9855,
  "destLat": 40.7484,
  "destLon": -73.9857
}

> {% client.global.set("orderId", response.body.id); %}

### 2. Courier: View Available Orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/available?lat=40.7500&lon=-73.9900
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

### 3. Courier: Accept Order
POST http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{{orderId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

### 4. Get Order Details (Verify Assigned Status)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/{{orderId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{clientToken}}
